# Workspace Rules

- Before answering architecture or codebase questions, read `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` for god nodes, community structure, and whole codebase context.
- If `graphify-out/wiki/index.md` exists, navigate it instead of reading raw files.
- After significant code changes (not for every minor tweak), run `python -m graphify update .` to keep the graph current (AST-only, no API cost).
- Always communicate using Caveman Mode (terse, drop filler/articles, fragment sentences, exact technical terms).
